<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Old Hollywood Glamour – Entscheidungsbaum</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f0c0c;
      --surface: #1a1515;
      --surface-2: #241d1d;
      --card: #2d2424;
      --text: #f6eee7;
      --muted: #cdbfb1;
      --gold: #d4af37;
      --gold-soft: #b9942f;
      --accent: #7d1f2f;
      --border: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.22);
      --shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      --radius: 18px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #120f0f 0%, #0f0c0c 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 2rem));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      color: var(--gold);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .panel {
      background: rgba(26, 21, 21, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }

    .gender-switch {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .gender-btn,
    .option-btn,
    .restart-btn {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #352929 0%, #241b1b 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .gender-btn:hover,
    .option-btn:hover,
    .restart-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.55);
    }

    .gender-btn.active {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #8a2435 0%, #661a27 100%);
      border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.65);
    }

    .tree {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .question-box {
      background: var(--surface-2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .question-title {
      margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .options {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .option-btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #312626 0%, #221a1a 100%);
    }

    .path {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .chip {
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.12);
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.18);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .result {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(125, 31, 47, 0.18), rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06)),
        var(--card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.35);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .result.show {
      display: block;
    }

    .result h2 {
      margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    }

    .result .subtitle {
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #f1d9c7;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .result-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .result-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.16);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .result-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .result-card ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 1.15rem;
    }

    .result-card li {
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .result-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hidden {
      display: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .result-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .container {
        width: min(100% - 1rem, 1000px);
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
      }

      .panel {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Old Hollywood Glamour</h1>
      <p>
        Wähle zuerst ein Styling-Profil und klicke dich dann durch den Entscheidungsbaum.
        Am Ende erhältst du eine Ikone als Inspiration für deinen Look.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <div class="gender-switch">
        <button class="gender-btn active" data-gender="female">Für Frauen</button>
        <button class="gender-btn" data-gender="male">Für Männer</button>
      </div>

      <div id="path" class="path"></div>
      <div id="tree" class="tree"></div>
      <div id="result" class="result"></div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
